sentences.sentence: Community is vibrantly alive in my neighborhood!
sentences.translation: 社区是我家附近最具生机的事物！

sentences.sentence: How are things then when the body flow is fully and vibrantly under way?
sentences.translation: 事物是怎样的，当身体流动时完全，充满活力的在进行中？

sentences.sentence: New Guinea has some of the most beautiful freshwater fish found anywhere, including tiny and vibrantly colored rainbow fish, according to WWF.
sentences.translation: 在新几内亚岛，许多地方都生活有最漂亮的淡水鱼，包括微小但充满活力的彩虹鱼，据世界野生生物基金会说。
